               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400817-name-383" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-383" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-383" type="surname" value="CHIGNELL"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-383" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES CHIGNELL</persName>
                  </hi>. I was in the employ of William White and others, carpet and rug manufacturers in Blackfriars-road—the prisoner was their porter. On the 13th of June I entered three hearth-rugs in the day-book, and delivered them to the packers to go to Farebrother, at Banbury.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400817-name-384" type="witnessName">
