                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-384" type="given" value="NATHNIEL"></interp>NATHNIEL DOYLE</persName>
                  </hi>. I packed the rugs, and sent them by the prisoner to the King's Arms, Holborn-bridge, directed to William Farebrother, Banbury.</p>
